            and Charges) Regulation</docTitle><sourceNote>(<ref href="hk/2020/ln37">L.N. 37 of 2020</ref>)</sourceNote><enactingFormula role="empoweringSection">(<ref href="/hk/cap498/s27">Cap. 498, section
                27(1)</ref>)</enactingFormula><sourceNote>(Enacting provision omitted—<ref href="/hk/2017/er4">E.R. 4 of
            2017</ref>)<marker role="blank-line"></marker><marker role="blank-line"></marker></sourceNote><commencementNote>[22 May 1997]<sourceNote><inline class="width_3"> </inline><ref href="/hk/1997/ln269">L.N. 269 of 1997</ref></sourceNote></commencementNote><sourceNote>(Format changes—<ref href="/hk/2017/er4">E.R. 4 of 2017</ref>)</sourceNote><section id="ID_1438403273158_001" name="s1" reason="repealed" startPeriod="2020-12-27" status="repealed" temporalId="s1"><num value="1">1.</num><sourceNote>(Repealed <ref href="hk/2020/ln37">L.N. 37 of 2020</ref>)</sourceNote></section><section id="ID_1438403273174_001" name="s2" reason="repealed" startPeriod="2020-12-27" status="repealed" temporalId="s2"><num value="2">2.</num><sourceNote>(Repealed <ref href="hk/2020/ln37">L.N. 37 of 2020</ref>)</sourceNote></section><section id="ID_1438403273174_003" name="s3" reason="repealed" startPeriod="2020-12-27" status="repealed" temporalId="s3"><num value="3">3.</num><sourceNote>(Repealed <ref href="hk/2020/ln37">L.N. 37 of 2020</ref>)</sourceNote></section><section id="ID_1438403273190_002" name="s4" reason="repealed" startPeriod="2020-12-27" status="repealed" temporalId="s4"><num value="4">4.</num><sourceNote>(Repealed <ref href="hk/2020/ln37">L.N. 37 of 2020</ref>)</sourceNote></section><section id="ID_1438403273205_001" name="s5" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2017-11-16" status="operational" temporalId="s5"><num value="5">5.</num><heading>Escort fees</heading><subsection id="ID_1438412740843_050" name="1" temporalId="s5_1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content>Where a vehicle is required to be escorted within any part of the Area, the provision of the escort service is subject to payment of the appropriate fee specified in column 3 of <ref>Schedule 3</ref>, by the person requesting the service, to the Commissioner or an operator, as may be appropriate.</content></subsection><subsection id="ID_1438412740859_005" name="2" temporalId="s5_2"><num value="2">(2)</num><leadIn>A fee payable under subsection (1) may be collected by the Commissioner or an operator, as may be appropriate—</leadIn><paragraph id="ID_1438412740859_013" name="a" temporalId="s5_2_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>in cash; or</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438412740859_021" name="b" temporalId="s5_2_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>in such other manner as determined by the Commissioner for the time being for the purposes of this paragraph.</content></paragraph></subsection></section><section id="ID_1438403273205_003" name="s6" reason="repealed" startPeriod="2020-12-27" status="repealed" temporalId="s6"><num value="6">6.</num><sourceNote>(Repealed <ref href="hk/2020/ln37">L.N. 37 of 2020</ref>)</sourceNote></section><section id="ID_1438403273221_002" name="s7" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2017-11-16" status="operational" temporalId="s7"><num value="7">7.</num><heading>Processing and permit fees</heading><subsection id="ID_1438412740905_020" name="1" temporalId="s7_1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content>The applicant for a permit shall pay to the Commissioner or an operator, as may be appropriate, the appropriate fee specified in column 3 of <ref>Schedule 5</ref> in respect of the issue of any permit by the Commissioner, or by the operator with the approval of the Commissioner in accordance with the terms of a management agreement.</content></subsection><subsection id="ID_1438412740905_028" name="2" temporalId="s7_2"><num value="2">(2)</num><leadIn>An applicant for a permit shall pay to the Commissioner or an operator, as may be appropriate, for processing an application for a permit of a description or in respect of a type or class of vehicle specified by the Commissioner, a fee determined by the Commissioner—</leadIn><paragraph id="ID_1438412740921_005" name="a" temporalId="s7_2_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>in consultation with the Director; and</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438412740921_013" name="b" temporalId="s7_2_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>with reference to the type or class of vehicle,</content></paragraph><continued>and such fee shall be payable—</continued><paragraph id="ID_1438412740921_027" name="i" temporalId="s7_2_i"><num value="i">(i)</num><content>in addition to the fee referred to in subsection (1) (where a permit is issued); and </content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438412740921_035" name="ii" temporalId="s7_2_ii"><num value="ii">(ii)</num><content>whether or not the permit is issued.</content></paragraph></subsection><subsection id="ID_1438412740921_042" name="3" temporalId="s7_3"><num value="3">(3)</num><leadIn>A fee payable under subsection (1) or (2) may be collected by the Commissioner or an operator, as may be appropriate—</leadIn><paragraph id="ID_1438412740921_050" name="a" temporalId="s7_3_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>in cash; or</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438412740921_058" name="b" temporalId="s7_3_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>in such other manner as determined by the Commissioner for the time being for the purposes of this paragraph.</content></paragraph></subsection></section><section id="ID_1438403273236_001" name="s8" reason="inEffect" startPeriod="2020-12-27" status="operational" temporalId="s8"><num value="8">8.</num><heading>Fees and charges for removal, impounding and storage</heading><subsection id="ID_1438412740952_004" name="1" temporalId="s8_1"><num value="1">(1)</num><leadIn>The owner of a vehicle shall pay to the Commissioner or an operator, as may be
                appropriate, the appropriate fee or charge specified in column 3 of <ref>Schedule
                    6</ref> in respect of—</leadIn><paragraph id="ID_1438412740952_012" name="a" temporalId="s8_1_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>the removal;</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438412740952_020" name="b" temporalId="s8_1_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>the removal and storage; or</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438412740952_028" name="c" temporalId="s8_1_c"><num value="c">(c)</num><content>the impounding,</content></paragraph><continued>of the vehicle under <ref>section 22</ref> or <ref>23</ref> of the
                Ordinance.</continued></subsection><subsection id="ID_1438412740952_041" name="2" temporalId="s8_2"><num value="2">(2)</num><leadIn>A fee or charge payable under subsection (1) may be collected by the
                Commissioner or an operator, as may be appropriate—</leadIn><paragraph id="ID_1438412740952_049" name="a" temporalId="s8_2_a"><num value="a">(a)</num><content>in cash; or</content></paragraph><paragraph id="ID_1438412740952_057" name="b" temporalId="s8_2_b"><num value="b">(b)</num><content>in such other manner as determined by the Commissioner for the time being
                    for the purposes of this paragraph.</content></paragraph></subsection><subsection id="ID_1438412740952_064" name="3" temporalId="s8_3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content>Any person who fails to pay a fee or charge payable under subsection (1) within
                21 days of a demand being made for it commits an offence.</content></subsection><subsection id="ID_1607673248196_001" name="4" temporalId="s8_4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content>A person who commits an offence under subsection (3) is liable on conviction to
                a fine at level 2 and to imprisonment for 6 months. <sourceNote>(<ref href="hk/2020/ln37">L.N. 37 of 2020</ref>)</sourceNote></content></subsection></section><section id="ID_1438403273236_003" name="s9" reason="repealed" startPeriod="2020-12-27" status="repealed" temporalId="s9"><num value="9">9.</num><sourceNote>(Repealed <ref href="hk/2020/ln37">L.N. 37 of 2020</ref>)</sourceNote></section><schedule id="ID_1438403273252_002" name="sch1" reason="repealed" startPeriod="2020-12-27" status="repealed" temporalId="sch1"><num value="1">Schedule
